740
01:41:47,375 --> 01:41:49,808
Ne upiri to u mene, napunjeno je.

741
01:41:54,132 --> 01:41:59,079
Glenda Hil je prototip ukusa, zasto
nisi pristala.

742
01:41:59,690 --> 01:42:02,044
